{"tid":566746,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港賀歲票房：梁朝偉可能不敵劉嘉玲","createTime":"2018-02-20T08:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T13:31:53.000Z","uid":134071,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"30069654f4840cf6061ddcb990eee2306d209de1","tid":566746,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"估唔到《捉妖記2》香港頭一日票房都有290萬， 師奶真係好支持梁朝偉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但睇黎《捉妖記2》香港口碑都好差下，票房日日大降， 埋單香港票房可能會輸比劉嘉玲主演既《我的情敵女婿》。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   （不過《捉妖記2》主要市場係大陸。）<br />\n<br />\n仲記得黃子華曾經感嘆過: 梁朝偉可以經常被邀請拍&quot;果D&quot; 好片, 黃子華自己就經常被邀請拍&quot;呢D&quot; 渣片。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （子華話自己唯有&ldquo;慳D&rdquo;， 一度放棄電影而專注舞台演出。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/59967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F59967&d=O5GDw088ZA10p07MbgUQiU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=ed619d4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/59967</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/160936_3b75a492f9c8c1c99b752ef50979823f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F160936_3b75a492f9c8c1c99b752ef50979823f.jpg&h=ab71db3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/161012_cd6a86e98a0f60ddac1419c3eb280e91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F161012_cd6a86e98a0f60ddac1419c3eb280e91.jpg&h=64acf662&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49bde8a5f38e45ac36af540429dab60508095a20","tid":566746,"uid":61903,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T08:14:13.000Z","msg":"一家大哂冇份<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ec1c699916f3b0065ada145a354cc760ef3d59","tid":566746,"ui