拍&quot;呢啲&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T13:31:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://www.dayo-wong.com/sc/magazine/%E9%BB%83%E5%AD%90%E8%8F%AF-%E5%86%87%E7%B1%AE%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dayo-wong.com%2Fsc%2Fmagazine%2F%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%258F%25AF-%25E5%2586%2587%25E7%25B1%25AE%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2594%259F%2F&d=O5GDw088ZA10p07MbgUQiU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=5d582043\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.dayo-wong.com/sc/magazine/%E9%BB%83%E5%AD%90%E8%8F%AF-%E5%86%87%E7%B1%AE%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%9F/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n換個角度，一切只是相對，「懷着夢想攀向高峰，原來已在下山途中」是他的電影夢寫照。圈中人認定華仔偉仔是「嗰啲」質素，子華只有「呢啲」，「其實我都推咗幾部『呢啲』，但「嗰啲」又唔會搵我『呢啲』，最後自己慳啲！」此路不通，他終於承認：「唔做電影，咪做棟篤笑囉！」"}]}